      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in a pristine, factory-fresh state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own an example of this model in truly investment-grade condition, requiring absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
