      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you! It runs super smoothly and looks great\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
