    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This high-compression engine features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp engagement, feeding power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and well-sorted dampers. While the exterior displays minor patina, the 8,000 RPM redline remains exhilarating and the throttle response is telepathic. A true enthusiast's specimen focused on longitudinal and lateral performance.",
