      "description": "This 2019 Lexus RX 350 is a meticulously maintained luxury SUV that perfectly balances performance and comfort. Finished in a sophisticated Atomic Silver, the exterior retains a deep gloss, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is in excellent shape, free of tears or heavy stains, and the cabin still feels like a quiet sanctuary. Every feature, from the heated and ventilated seats to the intuitive navigation system, works perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust; it has a complete service history with all oil changes and inspections performed on schedule. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. If you are looking for a reliable, honest vehicle that has been treated with respect, this RX 350 is an exceptional choice.",
